snippet.title: Jonah Lobe
snippet.description:
Are you interested in art, fantasy, and world-building?  If so, this is the channel for you.

I'm Jonah Lobe - I'm an Artist, Educator, Author and Game Designer.  You might know me from my work on such games as Skyrim and Fallout.  My purpose on YouTube is to become a resource for you, the aspiring world-builder.  To that end, I'll be releasing a series of inspirational, art-focused videos meant to aid artists and imagineers of all kinds.  So don't hesitate - follow me... and let's build worlds together.
